N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1097.9 - Presentation of tickets

State Regulations

No person shall refuse or fail to present a valid LIRR
ticket, employee pass or dependent pass, or tender the applicable fare, as
required. Notes
